channel.title: New-World ~Next #1 RSPS~
channel.description:
Welcome To New-World ~ The Next #1 RSPS online !
~Features~
-Server Is on a fully working VPN so no lag -Just like Old-School Runescape -Pking based server but also a great eco! -Very Friendly staffs!! -PVP is as good as PVM so it suits all players! -We need staffs -First two weeks donations give 3X the points per dollar -Donator Island Is still under construction but it'll be awesome :D ~~~~~Minigames~~~~~ -Fully Working Pest Control -Jad for firecape -Working Barbarian Assault -Currently Working On Barrows -100% Working Duel Arena -New Working Warrior's Guild!
-Every City Teleports are working!
~~~~~Bossing~~~~~ -A ton of bosses are available for every player! -Fully working Godwars with every boss -Custom bosses in the wilderness ~~~~~Pking~~~~~ -As I said, it's mainly a Pking server so it's really good :) -Every skill is working under the Skilling tab
If you want to know more, come and see a staff will most likely be able to answer you :)
I hope to see you guys in-game! No pics for now
Link for download: http://new-world.boards.net/
